## Local environment example
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values for local development.

# Postgres connection used by migrations (example):
POSTGRES_URL=postgres://user:password@localhost:5432/mydb

# Set to true in CI to run migrations during build:
# RUN_MIGRATIONS=true

# Other env variables used by the app (examples):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_KEY=your_public_key
# NODE_ENV=development
